511
00:20:47,230 --> 00:20:49,470
Maksudku, semua begitu tersusun.

512
00:20:50,050 --> 00:20:50,930
Tersusun?

513
00:20:51,320 --> 00:20:54,000
Mungkin memang bisa dibilang begitu.

514
00:20:54,000 --> 00:20:59,780
